Package: dansal
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: ademant <ademant@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: adduser
Recommends: fail2ban
Description: Dance event calendar server
 Dansal is a REST API server for managing folk and balfolk dance events.
 It supports iCal feed import (with RRULE expansion), a JSON feed type for
 folkdance.page, per-event organisations, image attachments, magic-link
 login, and Prometheus metrics.
Section: web
Priority: optional
